<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>レコード出品アシスタント</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .header-container { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .header-container p { margin: 0; }
        .category-group { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
        .category-group label { font-weight: 600; white-space: nowrap; }
        .category-select { padding: 5px 8px; font-size: 14px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px; }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .form-group label { display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: 600; }
        .url-input { width: 100%; padding: 10px; font-size: 16px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>レコード出品アシスタント</h1>
        
        <form action="/process" method="POST">
            <div class="header-container">
                <p>Google Driveの親フォルダURLを入力して、出品データを生成します。</p>
                <div class="category-group">
                    <label for="defaultCategory">デフォルトカテゴリー:</label>
                    <select id="defaultCategory" name="defaultCategory" class="category-select">
                        <% if (categories && categories.length > 0) { %>
                            <% categories.forEach(category => { %>
                                <option value="<%= category.id %>"><%= category.name %></option>
                            <% }); %>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <option value="">カテゴリー読込失敗</option>
                        <% } %>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="parentFolderUrl">Google Drive 親フォルダURL</label>
                <input type="text" id="parentFolderUrl" name="parentFolderUrl" class="url-input" placeholder="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/..." required>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn">解析を開始</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
